  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"y equals 3 x plus 9\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"3 y equals 8 x minus 6\"><mn>3</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The solution to the given system of equations is&nbsp;<math alttext=\"left parenthesis x comma y right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>. What is the value of <math alttext=\"x minus y\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t<mo>-</mo>\n\t<mi>y</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math>?</p>",
