ds <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y equals 3 left parenthesis negative 33 right parenthesis plus 9\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>(</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>33</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn></math>,&nbsp;or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y equals negative 90\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>90</mn></math>. Substituting <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"negative 33\"><mo>-</mo><mn>33</mn></math> for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"negative 90\"><mo>-</mo><mn>90</mn></math> for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y\"><mi>y</mi></math> into the expression <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x minus y\"><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>y</mi></math> yields <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"negative 33 minus left parenthesis negative 90 right parenthesis\"><mo>-</mo><mn>33</mn><mo>-</mo><mo>(</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>90</mn><mo>)</mo></math>, or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"57\"><mn>57</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice A is incorrect. This is the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x plus y\"><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x minus y\"><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>y</mi></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice B is incorrect. This is the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x minus y\"><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>y</mi></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>",
